****************Infrastructure lifecycle ********************

day 0: plan and design 
day 1: develop and iterate 
day 2: golive and maintain 


+++++++++++ 1. reliability 
            2. idempoten


provisioning : make a server ready with systems, data and software for operations.. puppet , ansible, chef.
deployment: aws codepipeline, jenkins
orchestration: coordinating multiple systems, kubernetes


configuration drift:
configuration change when provisioning 
detect : aws config, azure policies, gcp secuirty health analytics, aws cloudformation drift detection , terraform state files 
fix: compliance tools like aws config , terraform refresh and plan commands, manual correction 
prevent: immutable infrastructure , never delete the server created . instead release a new version 



mutable and immutable infrastrcuture:

develop---> deploy ----> configure(cloud-init)
develop----> configure---> deployy 




